# The Comparison Report
# AI reads two versions of a contract and summarizes what changed between them.

[var: SITE = https://microsoft.sharepoint-df.com/teams/ZachDemos/]
[var: LIBRARY = https://microsoft.sharepoint-df.com/teams/ZachDemos/Contracts/]
[category: Documents & Files]

[section: setup]

Verify the "Contracts" library exists with two files: Northwind-MSA-v1.docx
and Northwind-MSA-v2.docx. This demo is read-only.

[navigate: ${LIBRARY}]

[open-chat]

[new-chat]

Confirm both contract versions are visible and the chat pane is fresh.

[pause]

[section: demo]

[navigate: ${LIBRARY}]

Legal just sent over the revised MSA. You could open both documents side by
side and read every clause... or you could let AI do the comparison in seconds.

[pause]

[open-chat]

[prompt: Compare Northwind-MSA-v1 and Northwind-MSA-v2. List every change and tell me which ones favor us and which ones favor the vendor.]

[wait]

Copilot caught all the changes: term extended from 12 to 24 months, payment
terms tightened from Net 45 to Net 30, liability cap doubled, termination
notice shortened, SLA improved, data residency expanded, non-compete halved,
and a new insurance requirement added. It also flagged who each change
benefits. Point out the favor analysis.

[pause]

Now let's go a step further — don't just compare, advise.

[prompt: Which changes should I push back on before signing?]

[wait]

It's not just comparing — it's advising. Copilot identified the most
consequential changes and suggested negotiation priorities. That's the jump
from search to intelligence.

[pause]

[screenshot: tools/screenshots/04-comparison-report-final.png]

[section: reset]

This demo is read-only. Just start a new chat.

[new-chat]
